## Session Management

### Resume (New in v4.2)
- Uses Claude CLI's built-in session management (`--session-id`, `--resume`)
- Full conversation context preserved (no transcript reconstruction)
- Works for both brainstorm and automated steps
- API errors auto-retry instead of failing

### How It Works
1. Sessions start with `--session-id <uuid>`
2. Session ID saved to `.pipeline/session-id`
3. Resume with `./pipeline resume <project>`
4. Claude restores full conversation context

