## Self-Improvement System (v4.8)

The pipeline learns from itself and continuously improves through cross-run intelligence.

### The Loop

```
Run Pipeline → Analyze → Archive → Detect Patterns →
                                            ↓
                      Cross-Run Analysis (query all archives)
                                            ↓
                      Calculate R&D Value (frequency × struggle)
                                            ↓
           ┌────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┐
           ↓                                                                ↓
    SUCCESS (quality ≥ 85%)                                    STRUGGLE (R&D value ≥ 80)
    → Extract code to module                                   → Generate improved module
           ↓                                                                ↓
           └────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘
                                            ↓
                          Save to ~/.pipeline/modules/
                                            ↓
                      Future Runs Use Better Modules
                                            ↓
                      Higher Quality → Faster → Cheaper (repeat)
```

