| `./pipeline learn show` | Display all learnings |
| `./pipeline learn add` | Record a fix interactively |
| `./pipeline learn detect <project>` | Auto-detect fixes from git |
| `./pipeline anti show` | List anti-patterns |
| `./pipeline anti clear <id>` | Remove an anti-pattern |

### Data Storage

```
~/.pipeline/
├── modules/                    # Module library
│   ├── catalog.json
│   └── <module-id>/
├── anti-patterns.json          # Failure patterns
├── module-feedback.json        # Usage outcomes
├── module-compositions.json    # Module pairs
├── learned-guidelines.json     # Human corrections
└── analysis-archive/           # Historical analysis
```

